File System Management for Wintermute
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Introduction

As defined in the document "File Systems and Wintermute" by the Synthetic Intell
ect Institute, Wintermute needs to have full control over the file system. In fa
ct, Wintermute will have to not organize files; it'll have to remove the "file
dialog" paradigm presented since the advent of "file cabients" on computers.

